<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Parañaque City - GreenGo</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 300px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            color: white;
        }

            .hero::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                bottom: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
                z-index: 1;
            }

            .hero h1, .hero p {
                position: relative;
                z-index: 2;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 56px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero p {
                max-width: 900px;
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 1.7;
                opacity: 0.95;
                text-align: justify;
            }

        /* Main Content */
        .content {
            padding: 50px 5%;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .category-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 40px 0 25px;
        }

        /* Cards Grid */
        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-4px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            }

        .card-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 60px;
            color: white;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .card-location {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .card-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .card-rating {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .rating-stars {
            color: #ffa000;
        }

        .rating-value {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .rating-count {
            color: #999;
        }

        .card-price {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .price-free {
            color: #5a8a3a;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #3d4f2f;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero" style="background-image: url('');">
        <h1>Parañaque City</h1>
        <p>Parañaque has a strong cultural identity with parish museums and military displays near Villamor. Plenty of community parks and green areas to explore.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Explore all places in Parañaque City</h2>

        <h3 class="category-title">Museum</h3>
        <div class="cards-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image">⛪</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Baclaran</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Baclaran Church Museum</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(religious)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image">🏛️</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Parañaque</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Parañaque Heritage Museum</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(local)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image">✈️</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Villamor</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Air Force Museum (Villamor)</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(military)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image">⛪</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Parañaque</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Mary Help of Christians Parish Mini Museum</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(parish)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="category-title">Parks</h3>
        <div class="cards-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#56ab2f 0%, #a8e063 100%);">🌳</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Parañaque</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Parañaque Community Park</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(community)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#56ab2f 0%, #a8e063 100%);">🌳</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">BF Homes</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">BF Homes Park</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(neighborhood)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#56ab2f 0%, #a8e063 100%);">🌿</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">Parañaque</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">Elizalde Park</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(local)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#56ab2f 0%, #a8e063 100%);">🌳</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-location">San Dionisio</p>
                    <h4 class="card-name">San Dionisio Park</h4>
                    <div class="card-rating"><span class="rating-stars">★★★☆☆</span><span class="rating-value">—</span><span class="rating-count">(community)</span></div>
                    <p class="card-price price-free">Free</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">© 2025 GreenGo NCR - Eco Travel Hub</footer>
</body>
</html>